caption: this morning I was on vine and I stumbled upon a performance video of Jack & Jack. (as always) but this time it was special. as I watched G asked the crowd how many of them ever felt alone or like lonely, everyone raised their hand. Then both of them said that all of us had them to turn to if we needed anything and that they will always be there. I am beyond thankful to have you and ugh I don't know what I'd do without you. brb gonna go cry now...
song_album: The Fault In Our Stars (Music From the Motion Picture)
